This is a list of episodes for ''[[The Daily Show|The Daily Show with Jon Stewart]]'' in 2015.<ref name=interbridge>{{cite web|title=The Late Night TV Page - Talk Show Guest Listings|url=http://www.interbridge.com/lineups.html#DS|work=interbridge}}</ref><ref name=tvdb>{{cite web|title=The Daily Show with Jon Stewart: Complete Episode List|url=http://thetvdb.com/?tab=seasonall&id=71256&lid=7|work=thetvdb}}</ref> This is the final year of ''The Daily Show'' to be hosted by Jon Stewart, whose final episode is scheduled for August 6, 2015. On February 10, 2015 he announced that he will retire at a later time in the year,<ref name="O'Neal">{{cite news|last1=O'Neal|first1=Sean|title=Jon Stewart says heâ€™s leaving The Daily Show|url=http://www.avclub.com/article/jon-stewart-says-hes-leaving-daily-show-215070|accessdate=11 February 2015|publisher=[[A.V. Club]]|date=10 February 2015}}</ref> and in March 2015, Comedy Central announced that contributor [[Trevor Noah]] will become the host of ''The Daily Show'' following the departure of Stewart.<ref>[http://www.bbc.com/news/entertainment-arts-32114257 Trevor Noah to replace Jon Stewart on The Daily Show] [[BBC News]] 30 March 2015</ref>

